

<div class="section no-pad-bot" id="index-banner" style="background-color: #f5f8fa">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row center">
            <h5 class="header col s12 light" style="text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #ccc;">测测你的浙小商指数 - 第三题</h5>
            <div class="col s12">
                <div class="card horizontal">
                    <div class="card-image hide-on-small-and-down">
                        <img src="~/img/Photo/left_view.jpg" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-stacked">
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <p>早上从钱江湾46幢江景房12楼到体育场上体育课，假设你在早上8:00才起床。
                                <br/>
                            请问全速奔跑，最快需要多久才能在上课前到达体育场 ？</p>
                            <ul style="text-align: left; display: inline-block">
                                <li class="row" style="margin: auto;">
                                    <p class="left">
                                        <input class="with-gap" name="group" type="radio" id="test1" />
                                        <label for="test1">A.3分钟</label>
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="row" style="margin: auto;">
                                    <p class="left">
                                        <input class="with-gap" name="group" type="radio" id="test2" />
                                        <label for="test2">B.5分钟</label>
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="row" style="margin: auto;">
                                    <p class="left">
                                        <input class="with-gap" name="group" type="radio" id="test3" />
                                        <label for="test3">C.10分钟</label>
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="row" style="margin: auto;">
                                    <p class="left">
                                        <input class="with-gap" name="group" type="radio" id="test4" />
                                        <label for="test4">D.不要问我几分钟，我还在等电梯</label>
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-action">
                            <a href="@Url.Action("NextQuestion", new {cur = Model})">下一题</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
